Kingston Warehouse located at 71 Leichhardt Street, Kingston offers unique office accommodation not readily available in the market.  This small complex is situated in-between Barton and Fyshwick making it the ideal location for any occupier seeking a quieter fringe location.  The industrial theme of the available units differentiates itself from your traditional office space.

Public transport is available moments away and it is only a short drive to the city CBD, Canberra Airport and parliamentary Triangle.  There is an on site cafe and the Kingston Foreshore & Kingston Shops are in close proximity.

Unit 10 is available for lease 204sqm* in total split across ground (118sqm*) and mezzanine (86sqm*). 

Unit 3 is available for lease 204sqm* in total split across ground (124sqm*) and mezzanine (80sqm*).  

Both units feature the following;
- Air conditioning with exposed metal ducting
- Metal finishes on ceiling
- High ceiling with industrial high bay lighting
- Brand new timber flooring on the ground floor
- Large windows at the front of the unit
- New coat of paint
- Open plan configuration
- 2x unisex bathrooms
- Kitchenette
- 3x allocated parks

Suitable for a range of users especially anyone seeking creative space.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

Boasting high viability and exposure, 55 Wentworth Avenue is located within the exciting new Kingston Foreshore precinct which includes cafes, art galleries, glass works, harbour walk, gardens and residential mix.  Excellent accessibility to Public Transport with a bus stop directly out the front of the building, Bike and Walking Paths with further amenities nearby at Kingston/Manuka shops for banks, supermarkets, fashion, cafes and restaurants.  Centrally located it is only a short distance to the parliamentary triangle, City CBD and Canberra Airport

With excellent view on all floors, this prestige building offers the following vacancies;

Mezzaine, Suit 4 - 540sqm* - open plan layout and ready for fit out.

Level 2, Suite 5 - 1,856sqm* - partially fitted out tenancy

Level 3, Full Floor - 1,313sqm* - High quality, fully functional fit out in place with exceptional views from all angles.  Access to 3 exclusive balconies ready to move into.

Secure basement parking is available as well as generous visitor parking for clients.  This is a fantastic opportunity to be located in a quality building in an incredible location in the ACT.

For further information please contact the nominated representatives of CBRE Canberra.

The island at Kingston Foreshore is an exclusive precinct within Canberra's highly desirable lakeside community. This site is the last available on the Island, and enjoys a dominant position facing directly onto Kingston Harbour with views across the water to wetlands, parks and hills.

In this setting, you can create something unique. Zoned for mixed use, the site can accommodate up to 120 prestige dwellings, along with commercial premises along the harbour Promenade.

Kingston Foreshore puts residents close to the shopping and entertainment hubs of Kingston and Manuka, the parliamentary triangle and the city. Soon the harbourside Promenade will come to life with restaurants, cafes and specialty shops.

Occupying the entire northern frontage to the harbour, this site will become the centrepiece of Canberra's premier waterfront precinct.

The Land Development Agency invites tenders from suitably experienced and capable developers for the purchase of this superb waterfront development site, suitable for mixed use residential and commercial development.

TENDERS MUST BE SUBMITTED BY 2PM THURSDAY 5 SEPTEMBER 2013.
